      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW OSWALD (2) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 29.54 to score two back then following on with a 29.43 win over 515m at this track. Running fast times and looks the one to beat again. ELUSIVE CURL (4) flew the lids with a strong early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by 3 lengths over 515m at this track (29.43). Has a strong record from box 4, including two wins. Can make it two on the bounce. AVENGEMENT (6) produced a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 595m behind Nigel Devere (34.69) in a Special conditions H. Was a winner the start prior. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. PAW MATIC (3) has merit but will need to be at her best to take this out.",
